title: Hit Bengali Songs by Abhijit Bhattacharya & Udit Narayan | Hridayer Chhnoya | Bengali Modern Songs
description:
This jukebox is a compliation of Bengali songs, sung by eminent playback artistes Abhijit and Udit Narayan. The artistes need no introduction, as their singing styles are distinct with their respective persona. Do listen to their voice, in a language usually unusual than their own spheres. The lyrics are penned by Pulak Banerjee.
